<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.10">
<l>toṇṭīr pāṭumiṉō</l>
<l>curumpārppoḻil maṅkaiyarkōṉ</l>
<l>oṇṭār vēlkali yaṉoli mālaikaḷ</l>
<l>toṇṭīr pāṭumiṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, devotees, sing</l>
<l>The verse garlands of Kaliyaṉ with a bright, garlanded spear,</l>
<l>King of those of Maṅkai with bee-filled groves;</l>
<l>Oh, devotees, sing!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
